            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/smk/press-center/Press-releases/2010/developing-countries-must-do-more-to-rea.html?id=614648" title="">
                        Developing countries must do more to reach the Millenium Development Goals
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[20.09.2010]</p>
                <p>In his statement to the UN high-level meeting on the Millennium Development Goals, Norwegian Prime Minister Jens Stoltenberg stressed that developing countries bear the main responsibility for reaching the Millennium Development Goals.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
